text: Chiaki Sakanoue (born 20 September 1987) is a Japanese female water polo player who participated at the 2014 Asian Games, 2015 World Aquatics Championships, 2017 World Aquatics Championships, and 2019 World Aquatics Championships. == References == == Other websites == * Chiaki+Sakanoue zimbio * chiaki-sakanoue-jpn-water-polo alamy * chiaki-sakanoue-jpn-water-polo, alamy Category:1987 births Category:Living people Category:Japanese water polo players
